<DIV2 N="96" TYPE="chapter">
<HEAD>CHAP. XCVI.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">He is vi&s;ited by Pallet; contract, an intimacy with
a New-market nobleman; and is by the knowing|ones
taken in.</HEAD>
<P>THIS affair being &s;ettled, and our adventu|rer,
for the pre&s;ent, free of all female con|nexions,
he returned to his former cour&s;e of fa&s;t
wing, among the bucks of the town, and per|formed
<PB N="34" REF="40">
innumerable exploits among whores, bul|lies,
