<P>This prohibition, which announced his total
ruin, filled him with rage, horror and de&s;pair:
he cur&s;ed the porter who &s;ignified the mini&s;ter's
command, threatening to cha&s;ti&s;e him upon the
&s;pot for his pre&s;umption, and vented the mo&s;t vi|rulent
imprecations upon his ma&s;ter, to the a&s;to|ni&s;hment
